text: Byhåla (a derogative slang term for a boring village) is a comedy series featuring Ronny and Ragge, played by Fredde Granberg and Peter Settman. The series aired on SVT in 1991 to 1993. ==References== Category:Swedish comedy television series Category:1991 Swedish television series debuts Category:1993 Swedish television series endings Category:1990s Swedish television series
